Class MicrosoftScheduler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mpxj.cpm.MicrosoftScheduler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Scheduler

    public class MicrosoftScheduler
extends Object
implements Scheduler
    Implements the Critical Path Method to schedule a project so that the resulting schedule matches closely the results you'd see if you scheduled the same project in Microsoft Project.
